quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,1,“Alif-Lâm-Mîm
  3,2,"“Allah (ndimmodzi), palibe winanso wopembedzedwa mwa choonadi koma Iye Yekha, Wamoyo wamuyaya, Woimira ndi kuteteza chilichonse"
  3,3,"“Wakuvumbulutsira buku mwachoonadi, lomwe likutsimikizira zomwe zidalipo patsogolo pake. Ndipo adavumbulutsa Taurat ndi Injil"
  3,4,"“Kale, kuti (mabukuwo) akhale chotsogolera anthu. Ndipo adavumbulutsa (Qur’an) yolekanitsa pakati pa choonadi ndi chonama * Ndithudi, aja amene sadakhulupirire zizindikiro za Allah, adzakhala ndi chilango chaukali. Ndipo Allah Ngwamphamvu zoposa, Wobwezera (chilango mwaukali)"
  3,5,"“Ndithudi, kwa Allah sikungabisike chilichonse cha pansi ngakhale cha kumwamba"
  3,6,"“Iye ndi Yemwe amakulinganizani muli m’mimba mmaonekedwe anu mmene akufunira. Palibe wopembedzedwa mwachoonadi koma Iye; Ngwamphamvu zoposa, Ngwanzeru zakuya"
  3,7,"“Iye ndi Yemwe wakuvumbulutsira buku (ili la Qur’an), lomwe mkati mwake muli ndime zomveka zomwe ndimaziko a bukuli. Ndipo zilipo zina zokuluwika. Koma amene m’mitima mwawo muli kusokera, akutsata zomwe zili zokuluwika ndi cholinga chofuna kusokoneza anthu, ndi kufuna kudziwa tanthauzo lake lenileni. Palibe amene akudziwa tanthauzo lake lenileni koma Allah basi. Koma amene azama pa maphunziro, amanena: “Tawakhulupirira (ma Ayah amenewa). Onse ngochokera kwa Mbuye wathu.” Ndipo palibe angakumbukire koma eni nzeru basi"
  3,8,"“(Anzeruwo amanena): “ E Mbuye wathu! Musaikhotetse mitima yathu pambuyo potiongola. Tipatseni chifundo chochokera kwa Inu. Ndithudi, Inu Ndinu wopatsa kwambiri"
  3,9,"“E Mbuye wathu! Inu ndinu Wosonkhanitsa anthu patsiku lopanda chikaiko, ndithudi, Allah saswa lonjezo"